{"tid":2364486,"cid":37,"subCid":0,"title":"準過天文台｜馬鞍山3樓宇走廊地磚成「寒冷天氣指數」　10°C以下即脹起爆裂","createTime":"2021-01-13T04:42:31.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-13T07:39:17.000Z","uid":271829,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"d9caeb871486c38851815b48025170db43770bdf","tid":2364486,"uid":271829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-13T04:42:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/cPyCOmz1eBwUxGf9_YyZt8jHxds=/900x1600/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/I2R544C63BB2DEJEKE5KLX77QM.jfif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FcPyCOmz1eBwUxGf9_YyZt8jHxds%3D%2F900x1600%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FI2R544C63BB2DEJEKE5KLX77QM.jfif&h=cd6fbab3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n每逢冬天，欣安邨電梯走廊地磚均出現季節性「起伏」現象，地磚拱起呈波浪形。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/Nxx1iBPvfEtx5VArTymUv5D6fCQ=/3840x2160/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/EWWIEJULMJGVDDIT6PURQ7E7NM.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FNxx1iBPvfEtx5VArTymUv5D6fCQ%3D%2F3840x2160%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FEWWIEJULMJGVDDIT6PURQ7E7NM.JPG&h=d7b85de4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n有女居民表示前晚聽到走廊傳來爆裂聲，便知又是地磚爆裂。<br />\n<br />\n...<br />\n2011年入伙的馬鞍山欣安邨電梯走廊地磚，成為居民的「寒冷天氣指數」，過去10年每逢氣溫驟降或氣溫低於10度，地磚會脹起爆裂，三座無一倖免，沙田區議員容溟舟批評房署建屋工程質素參差，師傅鋪磚時太過「求其」，擔心有些爆磚凸起幾吋，絆倒老人家出意外。<br />\n<br />\n每逢冬天，欣安邨電梯走廊地磚均出現季節性「起伏」現象，地磚拱起呈波浪形，居民經過小心翼翼，一名女居民表示，前日晚上8時許聽到走廊傳來爆裂聲，知道又是地磚爆裂：「踩落去浮吓浮吓咁，老人家會危險啲。」<br />\n<br />\n區議員容溟舟表示，欣安邨現有三座欣喜、欣悅、欣頌樓，每一座逾10層出現不同程度的爆裂，其中欣悅樓更至少有三分之一的樓層走廊出現類似情況，形容爆磚甩瓦情況見慣不怪，直言：「好似欣安邨特產咁」。他稱，房署一直知道有關問題，亦有進行維修，因維修隊每星期只有三日駐守在欣安邨，其餘三日在水泉澳邨，加上疫情關係，修復工程緩慢，他擔心長者行動不便，行過凹凸不平的地磚容易跌倒，希望房署盡快處理好。<br />\n...<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20210112/GJ3HBCO5G5AVLCN7AKMQNHOY7Q/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20210112%2FGJ3HBCO5G5AVLCN7AKMQNHOY7Q%2F&d=Eu1QSTPz0OFPBNy7%2BevvEXG9l5Y5fMjkJfB04Oq%2Bkmk%3D&h=f4120ef1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20210112%2FGJ3HBCO5G5AVLCN7AKMQNHOY7Q%2F&h=047d0a1a\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20210112/GJ3HBCO5G5AVLCN7AKMQNHOY7Q/</a>"},{"pid":"6e7f7b194b196f52e3dd0620261d3f3054d35852","tid":2364486,"uid":73991,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-13T04:47:00.000Z","msg":"蝗蟲邨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e489a85fe1417ad6bff50c5d37ae24199f56f5e5","tid":2364486,"uid":36702,"like":15,"dislike":2,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-13T04:50:37.000Z","msg":"支那料  新移民師傅手工  <br />\n<br />\n係咁上下啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"213731d94eca02f59da362e31a0b10cd077c6c3a","tid":2364486,"uid":329466,"like":4,"dislike":7,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-13T04:52:29.000Z","msg":"公屋整都廢事喇 反正都係俾賤種垃圾住"},{"pid":"ca10eecc07065948d91a321f368dc3df4c3d78ec","tid":2364486,"uid":356602,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"213731d94eca02f59da362e31a0b10cd077c6c3a","tid":2364486,"uid":329466,"like":4,"dislike":7,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-13T04:52:29.000Z","msg":"公屋整都廢事喇 反正都係俾賤種垃圾住"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-13T04:53:55.000Z","msg":"你條死賤種幾時死？"},{"pid":"6129c4a1832833d3233944238b13c466a52f0f88","tid":2364486,"uid":40272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e489a85fe1417ad6bff50c5d37ae24199f56f5e5","tid":2364486,"uid":36702,"like":15,"dislike":2,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-13T04:50:37.000Z","msg":"支那料  新移民師傅手工  <br />\n<br />\n係咁上下啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-13T04:59:06.000Z","msg":"我想講私樓地盤都好多大陸人做<